Financial and Insurance Sector at Mantra HR Management Pvt. Ltd.
Posted by: Mantra HR Management Pvt. Ltd.
Posted date: 30-Apr
Job Description:Candidates will be a part of a new premier channel of "Our client" handpicked through a rigorous selection process.
Client will provide the candidates with a year long training program with minimal business expectation during the training period in order to develop them into a well rounded Sales Professional with holistic understanding of the Insurance industry.
This role will help the candidates develop their selling skills and develop into well rounded sales professionals proficient in Insurance sales.
Minimum Experience :- 2 Years (Should be from an industry with strong distribution focus (FMCG Pharma MLM etc) Any other sales experience will also be considered. Preferably from a Non Insurance sector
Competencies Required :-
